title: I got no S as Vayne
body: I had a perfect Kda as Vayne 29/0/6, along with other very good games and I haven't got 1 S yet towards lv 7? I am not quite sure how to send a photo to you but It will be on my match history. Please respond.

replies.body: Also I play another game a while ago and went 39/10/29 and got 1 pentakill and quada had 200 cs and 1v5 because my team started feeding because they were toxic and I won and I got an A-?
